    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PAIcom！最有趣、最棒的毛茸茸语音电脑助手！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[而且还是全球第一个毛茸茸（Protogen）语音助手！]<br><br>你可以用麦克风和他聊天！  <br>（作者小声说：真的和毛茸茸的烤面包机聊天超级开心！！1！）<br><br>他能帮你打开电脑上的应用、游戏、网站，还有更多功能！  <br><strong>(+ 他还能完全自定义/改装！)</strong><br><br><strong>PAIcom 尊重你的隐私（所有操作都在本地完成），不会向我们发送任何数据。</strong>  <br>（超级靠谱又逗比的家伙！！1！💯🔥）<br><br>支持桌面和 VR，有个超棒的 DISCORD 社区！  <br>（点击屏幕右侧的“Discord”按钮加入我们吧！:3）<br><br>=======================================================================&gt;  <br><br><i>那么……为什么要买 PAIcom？</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br><u><i><strong>他超搞笑！</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876280/extras/888d0a77c9cdc8b4abaa51571038e7c2.poster.avif?t=1768086447\" width=550 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876280/extras/888d0a77c9cdc8b4abaa51571038e7c2.webm?t=1768086447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876280/extras/888d0a77c9cdc8b4abaa51571038e7c2.mp4?t=1768086447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>而且还非常蠢萌 :3  <br>他对每个语音命令都有笑话！<br><br><u><i><strong>他超快！</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876280/extras/dc6184d09b0db0c562561a6ddb82999d.poster.avif?t=1768086447\" width=550 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876280/extras/dc6184d09b0db0c562561a6ddb82999d.webm?t=1768086447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876280/extras/dc6184d09b0db0c562561a6ddb82999d.mp4?t=1768086447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他在任何2012年及以后发布的电脑上都能飞快运行！  <br>只占用3%的CPU，和1.25%的内存！！  <br>来源：相信我，兄弟 &gt;w&lt;<br><br><u><i><strong>PAIcom 可以完全改装（不需要编程知识）</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876280/extras/54959f224f21a7b55b704e4a1cf5eab8.poster.avif?t=1768086447\" width=550 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876280/extras/54959f224f21a7b55b704e4a1cf5eab8.webm?t=1768086447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876280/extras/54959f224f21a7b55b704e4a1cf5eab8.mp4?t=1768086447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没错，你没听错！改装 PAIcom！  <br>你可以改名字、换皮肤、改回答、换声音，还有更多！  <br>你甚至可以用 PAIcom 的引擎自己做一个语音电脑助手！  <br><strong>是不是超级酷？</strong> :O  &lt;-- 顺便看你惊讶的表情<strong></strong><br><br><strong><i><u>兼容 Steam VR 和 SlimeVR</u></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876280/extras/4b11e84dd3edd713626a390c829e4b16.poster.avif?t=1768086447\" width=550 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876280/extras/4b11e84dd3edd713626a390c829e4b16.webm?t=1768086447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876280/extras/4b11e84dd3edd713626a390c829e4b16.mp4?t=1768086447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PAIcom 可以在 SteamVR 里以悬浮窗口出现！&gt;:3  <br>你可以让 PAIcom 改变你的 Steam 状态，打开 Steam/SteamVR，  <br>如果你在使用 SlimeVR 全身追踪游戏，PAlcom 还能帮你快速重新校准追踪器，防止漂移！<br><br>用 VR 控制器操作桌面很麻烦……  <br>所以 PAIcom 帮你快速搞定一切，不用费劲 :3<br><br><strong><i><u>那……你怎么负担得起这个？</u></i></strong>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876280/extras/44c140932baee1268862736a092dd892.poster.avif?t=1768086447\" width=299 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876280/extras/44c140932baee1268862736a092dd892.webm?t=1768086447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我负担不起啦哈哈哈。  <br>如果你想帮帮我，请考虑买下这个软件！':D<br><br>致谢：  <br>制作：Ovidiu Dendrino/scripter S  <br>配音：Ovidiu Dendrino/scripter S  <br>3D模型制作：Nukude，修改：Ovidiu Dendrino / scripter S  <br>Protogen物种设计：Malice-Risu (@CoolKoinu)  <br>SWU模型：Shadow_Hawk  <br>Deira模型：Mari  <br>Carnydrex模型：TheRPGslayer<br></p>",
